  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AddHoteleButton
    The AddHoteleButton class extends Button and provides functionality for adding a new hotel.
    AddKlientButton
    The AddKlientButton class extends Button and provides functionality for adding a new client (Klienci) to the system.
    AddListaHoteliButton
    The AddListaHoteliButton class extends Button and provides functionality for adding hotel lists to selected rooms for a chosen trip.
    AddMiastaButton
    The AddMiastaButton class extends Button and provides functionality to add a new city (Miasta) to the system.
    AddPokojButton
    The AddPokojButton class extends Button and provides functionality to add a new room (Pokoje) for a selected trip (Wycieczki).
    AddTypyWycieczekButton
    The AddTypyWycieczekButton class extends Button and provides the functionality to add a new trip type (TypyWycieczek) into the system, along with its associated pricing information (Ceny) and the assignment of cities for each night of the trip (MiastaWycieczek).
    AddWycieczkiButton
    The AddWycieczkiButton class extends Button and provides functionality for adding a new trip.
